cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a novel reinforcement learning algorithm that improves sample efficiency and enables learning in scenarios with both broad and sharp target context distributions. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on autonomous robots, which suggests that it may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the paper includes empirical evaluation using visual inputs, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category.
